# Text Line Processor Utility

This program processes strings based on the provided command-line options:
- `-h`: Prints help.
- `-c`: Counts the number of words in the input string.
- `-r`: Reverses the input string.
- `-w`: Prints each word in the string and its length.

## Compilation
To compile the program, run:

```bash
gcc -o stringfun test.c
